{
  "_comment": "Per-domain trainer system prompts for dataset-synth. Each preset is a `.md` file in this directory. `matchDomains` is the keyword list used by --preset auto to fuzzy-match a Qdrant payload's `domain` field. First match wins. `default` is the safety net.",
